*frei0r-plugins-1.1.22-r1 (05 Jul 2009)

  05 Jul 2009; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>
  -frei0r-plugins-1.1.22.ebuild, +frei0r-plugins-1.1.22-r1.ebuild,
  +files/frei0r-plugins-1.1.22-pkgconfig-support.patch:
